{"tid":1956012,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"口口聲聲話而家一百萬唔係錢，但要我搵又好撚難！","createTime":"2020-04-03T01:30:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T02:11:35.000Z","uid":156376,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"62054ab0e5d9ba7e880c7ad40e4edb0dc802f721","tid":1956012,"uid":156376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T01:30:42.000Z","msg":"係，以前有一百萬已經叫富翁，<br />\n但今時今日，一百萬真係眨吓眼就無左，<br />\n首期都唔夠比，叫百萬平民就差唔多.<br />\n但要搵一百萬，又好撚難（可能係我廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n當搵30k, 衣食住行家用集費起碼用左20k，<br />\n已經唔係大洗，當真係好叻仔，一個月儲一萬，<br />\n都要10年先有1球野，計返通脹，<br />\n到時嘅一百萬價值又可能得70萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到底出面係咪咁多人有一球野, 點搵返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申： 我廢，3x歲，銀行無6位數"},{"pid":"bab62407d983b707158d01d0406c1c0c3fcbe579","tid":1956012,"uid":162910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T01:32:41.000Z","msg":"呢度個個座底搵50k的<br />\n100萬2、3年就儲到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a7e84215c9842cba969e95300411cfeffb65581","tid":1956012,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T01:36:21.000Z","msg":"放個屁就洗哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23a2c87e0cbe41e74822a0de49ad66abce38e03d","tid":1956012,"uid":116723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62054ab0e5d9ba7e880c7ad40e4edb0dc802f721","tid":1956012,"uid":156376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T01:30:42.000Z","msg":"係，以前有一百萬已經叫富翁，<br />\n但今時今日，一百萬真係眨吓眼就無左，<br />\n首期都唔夠比，叫百萬平民就差唔多.<br />\n但要搵一百萬，又好撚難（可能係我廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n當搵30k, 衣食住行家用集費起碼用左20k，<br />\n已經唔係大洗，當真係好叻仔，一個月儲一萬，<br />\n都要10年先有1球野，計返通脹，<br />\n到時嘅一百萬價值又可能得70萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"